As Drive-By-Wire-Chassis/System Provider, Shanghai JIYU Technology Co., Ltd. was founded on July 2020, focusing on the R&D and production of the driverless chassis-by-wire for autonomous driving. 

Key products as below:
1) By-wire & Redundant Systems, including Redundant-Brake-by-wire / Redundant-Steering-by-wire / VCU / Parking-by-wire…;
2) By-wire-chassis platforms, with load capacity covering from 300kg to 6 tons, already deployed for various AD scenarios;
3) By-wire adaption for passenger cars, trucks, special vehicles. Especially offered redundancy brake system & steering-by-wire for famous USA truck company;
4) Skateboard Chassis, with four in-wheel motors, dual steering front & rear;
5) Autonomous driving EV charging robot (also Smart Energy Storage Unit).

Three series of by-wire-chassis platforms:
Shining Fairy 闪灵 S500 series, with payload 500kg;
Magic Carpet 魔毯 M3 series, with payload 1~3 tons;
Legendary Heracles 力牧 L6 series, with payload up to 5 tons.

The By-Wire-Chassis have been deployed for unmanned logistics, unmanned distribution, unmanned disinfection and sterilization, unmanned special vehicles, etc.

JIYU Technology just offers super running shoes for autonomous driving!

